Class FlightData

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--suncertify.client.FlightData
public class FlightData
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates a unit that describes a specified flight. Puts all the primitives in Object-derived class to easier data interchange.

Version:
1.2 26 Feb 2003
